---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroImage from '../components/HeroImage.astro';
import homeImage from '@assets/hero-images/palm-beach.webp';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from 'src/consts';
import PostTitle from '@components/PostTitle.astro';
import RecentPosts from '@components/RecentPosts.astro';
---

<Layout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
  <section class='max-w-5xl'>
    <PostTitle>Johnny & Leslie
     
    </PostTitle>
    <p class='text-lg md:text-xl lg:pr-5'>
      Follow our adventures, places and people we have visited and met in our
      trips.
    </p>
    <p class='my-8 text-xl font-bold uppercase'>Some details about us ðŸ˜€ :</p>

    <HeroImage class='rounded-lg' src={homeImage} alt={SITE_TITLE} />

    <div
      class='max-w-3xl mx-auto my-8 text-lg text-gray-700 flex flex-col space-y-3'
    >
      <p class='mt-8'>
        Welcome to the extraordinary journey of Leslie and Johnny, two
        passionate wanderers with an insatiable appetite for exploration and a
        taste for the extraordinary, through the vibrant tapestry of countries,
        cities, and cultures.
      </p>
      <p>
        From the bustling markets of Marrakech to the serene landscapes of New
        Zealand, we have traversed the globe, each adventure etching a unique
        chapter in their travelogue.
      </p>

      <p>
        But it's not just about the places; it's about the people. We believe in
        the transformative power of connecting with locals, savoring not just
        the flavors of exotic cuisines but the warmth of human stories.
      </p>
   

    <RecentPosts name={SITE_TITLE} />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>


